Package fi.sewsiaica.uusiaika.ui.viewpanels

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractViewPanel
    The abstract view panel currently contains the implementation of the createButtonPanel method.
    DoorToDoorViewPanel
    This class extends AbstractViewPanel; its object displays the door-to-door conversion view.
    GameOverViewPanel
    This class extends AbstractViewPanel; its object displays the game over view.
    LoadGameViewPanel
    This class extends AbstractViewPanel; its object displays the load a game view.
    MapViewPanel
    This class extends AbstractViewPanel; All the other views of the ActiveGame are reachable from the MapView.
    NewGameViewPanel
    This class extends AbstractViewPanel; its object displays the creation of a new game.
    OpeningMenuViewPanel
    This class extends AbstractViewPanel; its object displays the opening menu of the game.
    SettingsViewPanel
    This class extends AbstractViewPanel; its object displays the settings menu view.
    TempleViewPanel
    This class extends AbstractViewPanel; its object displays the temple view.
    TrainingCentreViewPanel
    This class extends AbstractViewPanel; its object displays the training centre view.
